The Brusselator source code has been forked from https://github.com/openmichigan/PSNM.
Its dependency - 2decomp_fft, has been downloaded from http://www.2decomp.org. Current version of 2decomp_fft is 1.5.847.

Run
---

Example:
`mpirun -np 4 ./Brusselator output nx ny nz steps plotgap(seconds)`

To add SZ compression (to the real parts only):
`mpirun -np 4 ./Brusselator output nx ny nz steps plotgap(seconds) sz accuracy global_accuracy`

where: 
	global_accuracy = 1e-4, 1e-5, etc.
